PN,37801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FThe parents of university student
OL,7,FBarnaby Webber, who was killed in the
OL,8,FNottingham attacks, said they started
OL,9,Fto panic as they tracked his phone,
OL,10,Fwatching it move to a police station.
OL,12,FThe 19-year-old student was stabbed to
OL,13,Fdeath by paranoid schizophrenic Valdo
OL,14,FCalocane in June 2023, alongside Grace
OL,15,FO'Malley Kumar. School caretake Ian
OL,16,FCoates also died in the attacks.
OL,18,FBarnaby's father David described
OL,19,Ftrying to reach his son after learning
OL,20,Fabout the attacks on the news, and the
OL,21,Fmoment he realised something was wrong.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FHe said: "We were getting up in the
OL,7,Fmorning. Emma had to work, I had to
OL,8,Fwork. I turned the TV on and saw the
OL,9,Fmedia light up.
OL,11,F"My first instinct was to message
OL,12,FBarney to see if he was OK. I messaged
OL,13,Fhim and got no response, so at one
OL,14,Fpoint I thought I'll phone him. So I
OL,15,Fphoned, still got no response which
OL,16,Fwas quite unusual because Barney would
OL,17,Fnormally answer the phone."
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FMr Webber said he checked Find My
OL,7,Fphone to see where he was, and could
OL,8,Fsee he was on Ilkeston Road but he was
OL,9,Fquite close to his student
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FHe added: "I phoned the police and
OL,13,Fsaid who I was and I said who my son
OL,14,Fwas, and I remember a distinct change
OL,15,Fin tone from the lady I was speaking
OL,16,Fto."
OL,26,@tD@KOUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FThe father added that the police said
OL,7,Fit was a "fast-changing scene" and
OL,8,F"there was no-one that could speak" to
OL,9,Fhim, but would call him back. He said
OL,10,Fthe phone started to move on the
OL,11,Ftracking app, and the parents "watched
OL,12,Fit go all the way to Radford Road
OL,13,Fpolice station", which is when they
OL,14,F"panicked". Mr Webber said: "I said
OL,15,F'we've got to go now', just said
OL,16,F'something is wrong'."
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@^O]pD@AOUpD@cO]sD@_OUuD@OO]vD@
OL,26,AAOUvD@JO]vD@]OUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FParents Emma and David Webber said
OL,7,Fthey were given very little
OL,8,Finformation about their son's killer,
OL,9,Fsaying they were only told he was also
OL,10,Fa student at the University of
OL,11,FNottingham when they attended a vigil
OL,12,Ftwo days later.
OL,14,FMrs Webber claimed there was also very
OL,15,Flittle information at a meeting with
OL,16,Fthe police chief constable three
OL,17,Fmonths after the attacks.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FShe said: "We were asking very clear,
OL,7,Fobvious questions about where he
OL,8,Flived, we wanted to know about his
OL,9,Fage, his background, and where did he
OL,10,Fwork? None of that was made available
OL,11,Fto us, was it?"
OL,13,FMrs Webber said she cannot "distinctly
OL,14,Frecall" any mention of Calocane's
OL,15,Fmental health in that meeting.
OL,17,FShe said officers whose job it was to
OL,18,Fsupport them after their son was
OL,19,Fstabbed to death were advocates for
OL,20,Fthe police, not for victims.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@OO]uD@\OUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FShe said: "As much as they are kind
OL,7,Fand caring, they are still there to
OL,8,Fadvocate for the police force... To
OL,9,Fhave no advocacy for you is something
OL,10,Fthat would need to be addressed."
OL,12,FShe added: "Nothing can be worse than
OL,13,Fbeing told, as a parent, that your
OL,14,Fchild is dead. So having to hear the
OL,15,Findividual who did it had a history
OL,16,Fand there were mistakes and clear
OL,17,Fevidence of police failures, even if
OL,18,Fyou don't want to hear it, I do think
OL,19,Fit needs to be put in writing so it is
OL,20,Fthere."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@aO]tD@LOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FMr Webber said it was important that
OL,7,Ffamilies of victims are told the
OL,8,Ftruth, adding: "It comes down to duty
OL,9,Fof candour ` tell the truth, just be
OL,10,Fhonest."
OL,12,FHe said: "If you are told the truth,
OL,13,Fwe are intelligent human beings, as
OL,14,Fmuch as it will hurt, it isn't going
OL,15,Fto hurt as much as the news that was
OL,16,Fdelivered on the 13th (of June 2023).
OL,17,FWe can't have a public inquiry every
OL,18,Ftime something like this happens, it
OL,19,Fhas to stop."
OL,26,@pD@POUrD@HO]tD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FThe parents of Barnaby and Grace are
OL,7,Fgiving evidence to the Nottingham
OL,8,Fattacks public inquiry.
OL,10,FUniversity of Nottingham friends
OL,11,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,12,FKumar were celebrating the end of
OL,13,Fexams when they were brutally killed
OL,14,Fon the way back to their student
OL,15,Faccommodation from a club in the early
OL,16,Fhours of the morning on 13 June, 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FCalocane then stabbed 65-year-old
OL,7,Fschool caretaker Ian Coates, who was
OL,8,Fon his way to work, before stealing
OL,9,Fhis van and using it to run over three
OL,10,Fother people.
OL,12,FThe inquiry, which is being held in
OL,13,Fcentral London, is examining the
OL,14,Fevents leading up to and after the
OL,15,Fattacks. Speaking at the start of the
OL,16,Fproceedings, Mrs Webber said the
OL,17,Finquiry "must expose the systemic
OL,18,Ffailures".
OL,26,@yD@IOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FShe had said: "It's not about isolated
OL,7,Ferrors. It's about whether the systems
OL,8,Fdesigned to protect the public are fit
OL,9,Ffor purpose, and they're not."
OL,11,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,12,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,13,F2024 after admitting three counts of
OL,14,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,15,Fresponsibility and three counts of
OL,16,Fattempted murder.
OL,18,FBarnaby Webber was remembered as a
OL,19,F"fun, friendly and full of life"
OL,20,Fstudent in his seminars by his tutors.
OL,26,@nD@OOUqD@^O]{D@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of student killed by Calocane
OL,4,Ctracked son's phone to police station
OL,6,FHis mother previously said he was
OL,7,F"obsessed with aeroplanes" and dreamed
OL,8,Fof becoming an RAF pilot. Ms O'Malley-
OL,9,FKumar, who was studying medicine, was
OL,10,Fdescribed by her family as a "truly
OL,11,Fwonderful and beautiful young lady"
OL,12,Ffollowing her death.
OL,14,FShe had played for England Hockey at
OL,15,Funder-16 and under-18 level, going on
OL,16,Fto represent her university in the
OL,17,Fsport.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@ZO]rD@^OUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
